\f0\b\fs34 \cf2 5. No-Shows and Non-Responsive Clients
\f1\b0\fs28 \
\
If a Client:\
\
a. fails to provide required information, documentation, or instructions;\
b. fails to respond to reasonable communications;\
c. fails to arrange or complete delivery of Cremated Remains; or\
d. otherwise prevents the Service from proceeding,\
\
we may:\
\
a. suspend or cancel the Booking; and\
b. retain all fees paid to cover administrative and operational costs,\
\
except to the extent required by law.\
\

