\f1\b0\fs28 \cf2 \
\
We may reschedule the Service where reasonably necessary, including due to:\
\
a. weather conditions;\
b. wind, visibility, or environmental conditions;\
c. aviation or airspace restrictions;\
d. aircraft availability or maintenance;\
e. safety concerns;\
f. regulatory requirements;\
g. delivery delays; or\
h. any other operational or logistical issue.\
\
Where we reschedule the Service:\
