\f0\b\fs34 \cf2 7. Weather, Safety, and Operational Delays
\f1\b0\fs28 \
\
All Services are subject to weather, safety, and operational conditions.\
\
We may delay, suspend, or reschedule a Service if we determine that proceeding would be unsafe, impractical, or unlawful.\
\
This includes (but is not limited to):\
\
a. adverse weather conditions;\
b. wind, turbulence, or visibility issues;\
c. aircraft or equipment limitations;\
d. air traffic control or airspace restrictions;\
e. environmental or safety concerns.\
\
Such delays do not entitle the Client to a refund.\
\

\f0\b\fs34 8. Force Majeure
\f1\b0\fs28 \
\
We are not liable for delay, rescheduling, or inability to perform the Service due to a Force Majeure Event.\
\
Force Majeure Events include, but are not limited to:\
\
a. weather events or natural disasters;\
b. fire, flood, or environmental hazards;\
c. pandemics or public health events;\
d. war, terrorism, or civil unrest;\
e. industrial action or labour shortages;\
f. government restrictions or regulatory changes;\
g. aviation disruptions;\
h. carrier or logistics failures;\
i. utility or communications outages.\
\
Where a Force Majeure Event occurs, we may:\
\
a. reschedule the Service;\
b. suspend the Booking; or\
c. cancel the Booking if performance is no longer reasonably practicable.\
\
Refunds or credits in such cases are at our discretion, except where required by law.\
\

\f0\b\fs34 9. Delivery Delays, Loss, or Improper Packaging
\f1\b0\fs28 \
\
\pard\tx560\tx1120\tx1680\tx2240\tx2800\tx3360\tx3920\tx4480\tx5040\tx5600\tx6160\tx6720\sl324\slmult1\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0

\f0\b\fs30 \cf2 9.1 Client responsibility
\f1\b0\fs28 \cf2 \
\
The Client is responsible for ensuring that Cremated Remains are:\
\
a. packaged correctly;\
b. labelled correctly; and\
c. sent in accordance with our instructions and applicable laws.\
\

\f0\b\fs30 \cf2 9.2 Carrier delays or loss
\f1\b0\fs28 \cf2 \
\
We are not liable for delays, loss, damage, or misdirection occurring during transport by third-party carriers.\
\
If remains are delayed or lost in transit:\
\
a. we may assist in reasonable enquiries with the carrier;\
b. the Booking may be delayed or suspended; and\
c. no refund is provided for carrier-related issues.\
\

\f0\b\fs30 \cf2 9.3 Improper packaging
\f1\b0\fs28 \cf2 \
\
If packaging does not comply with our requirements:\
\
a. we may refuse intake;\
b. we may delay or cancel the Booking;\
c. additional handling or remediation fees may apply; and\
d. no refund will be provided where the issue is caused by the Client.\
\
